author: {'steamid': '76561198194680793', 'num_games_owned': 3045, 'num_reviews': 1947, 'playtime_forever': 2535, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 2535, 'last_played': 1702003704}
review:
Несмотря на то, что в игре довольно примитивный геймплей, играть было интересно. Всё время хотелось побить рекорд (среди друзей сейчас первый). Игра действительно до невозможности простая. Вам нужно открывать картинки, зашифрованные цифрами 0 и 1. Все ваши действия просто нажимать кнопку, соответствующую цифре, в той последовательности, в какой они идут на экране. Чем быстрее это сделаете и чем больше откроете картинок, тем больше получите очков. В этом весь геймплей, где главная цель набрать наивысшее количество баллов. И делаете это под бодрую и весёлую музыку, которая как-бы подгонят вас.
В общем, простенькая аркада за которой можно неплохо так залипнуть. Именно своей простотой игра и подкупает.

author: {'steamid': '76561198201246082', 'num_games_owned': 3232, 'num_reviews': 1500, 'playtime_forever': 241, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 241, 'last_played': 1658266257}
review:
Chimpology, sizi internetin yavaş ve şempanzelerle dolu olduğu 1999 yılına geri götüren benzersiz ve ilginç bir oyundur. themorfeus tarafından geliştirilen ve Junkhive tarafından yayınlanan bu oyunda, resimleri sunucudan istemciye parça parça yönlendirmekten sorumlu bir korpo-şempanze yönlendirici rolünü üstleniyorsunuz.

Oyunda sadece iki düğme bulunuyor, ancak yönlendirilecek çok sayıda görüntü var, bu nedenle oyuncuların hızlı ve verimli olması gerekiyor. Ritimle veya ritimsiz oynayabilir ve kendi resimlerinizden bazılarını internet üzerinden aktarabilirsiniz. Chimpology klavye, gamepad, dancemat, gitar, arcade çubuğu, muz ve hatta yarı makine bir yunus dahil olmak üzere çeşitli giriş cihazlarıyla test edilmiştir.

Chimpology'nin en ilginç yönlerinden biri mizahı ve tuhaflığıdır. Oyunun hikayesi ve konsepti gerçekten benzersizdir ve geliştiriciler oyuncuları saatlerce meşgul edecek keyifli ve eğlenceli bir deneyim yaratmayı başarmışlardır.

Genel olarak Chimpology, farklı bir şeyler arayan oyuncular için mükemmel olan eğlenceli ve benzersiz bir oyundur. Basit ancak zorlu oynanışı, mizahı ve tuhaflığı ile birleştiğinde, her beceri seviyesinden oyuncu için keyifli bir deneyim haline getiriyor.

review:
Clicker enthousisast warning; you need to be able to press 2, i repeat: TWO keys to play this game.
Leaderboard fanatic warning; can be addictive for you only need to press two keys.
Banana lover warning; many banana's to win, but no, they're not "that" type of banana's. (Colorful banana's in the Steam Points Shop)
Fury fan warning; It's just you at a keyboard, no interaction with pictures of regular monkees.
Programmer warning; It's mindless robot work. A simple 4 or 6 line script will suffice to do the work for you. (Binary Profile Background in the Steam Points Shop)
Card farmer warning; Even if you can get it for sale, player base might be to small to sell or trade.
Perfect Game warning: You'll have to F-up 50 games to get that achievement.

author: {'steamid': '76561198796851430', 'num_games_owned': 927, 'num_reviews': 3722, 'playtime_forever': 6181, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 6181, 'last_played': 1647328483}
review:
首先我要表达我对Chimpology游戏玩法的不满。游戏以猿类为主题，玩家需要通过解决各种谜题和挑战来帮助猿类发展文明。然而游戏的谜题设计缺乏创意和多样性，让我感到乏味和重复。

其次游戏的操作和控制不够流畅，给玩家带来困扰。在游戏中我经常遇到操作响应不及时和动作不精确的问题，这使得解决问题和完成挑战变得困难，并影响了我的游戏体验。

再次故事情节缺乏吸引力。游戏的剧情发展平淡无奇，缺乏深度和引人入胜的情节。我很难对游戏中的角色和故事产生兴趣，难以投入到游戏的世界中。

另外游戏的图形和音效表现一般。游戏的视觉效果缺乏精细的细节处理，图像质量不够出色。音效方面，背景音乐和效果音不够丰富和逼真，无法为游戏增添足够的氛围和紧张感。

最后我还要提到游戏的售后。在游戏过程中，我遇到了一些技术问题，如游戏崩溃和控制失灵等。这些问题严重影响了我的游戏体验，并让我感到沮丧。

综上所述，作为一款以猿类文明发展为主题的游戏，玩法缺乏创意和多样性，操作不够流畅，故事情节平淡无奇，图形和音效表现一般。我建议玩家在购买前要考虑好自己的期望和口味，以免像我一样感到失望。对于喜欢策略和谜题游戏的玩家，我建议选择其他更加成熟和有趣的作品。

author: {'steamid': '76561198030784015', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 11208, 'playtime_forever': 2618, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 2618, 'last_played': 1579003183}
review:
Chimpology is a retro pixel button mashing game where you must hit the keys corresponding to "1" and "0" in sequence.  Get the numbers right and you can progress.  Enough mistakes and you lose.  For some reason they decided that despite having "0" and "1" keys on your keyboard, they should be "z" and "m" because apparently these guys never saw a keyboard before.

There's no other gameplay to speak of here.  Graphics are ugly.  The developers seem to have put more effort into explaining why their terrible game works the way it does (chimpanzees or something) than actually developing a game people might enjoy.  Totally not worth $3.

review:
"Chimpo"logyと聞いたら"Chimpo"の部分が頭から離れなくなったため、以下、ネタ文章 (閲覧注意)

[spoiler]ちんぽは、サーバーからクライアントへのぉおお画像をビットごとにルーティングしゅるのぉおお、有望にゃおﾞぉおォおちんぽルーターのぉおお役割を果たしゅるのぉおお。
ぁあああ あぉにゃたのぉおお使いぃ捨てのぉおおボタンは2ちゅしかにゃいぃのぉおおれ、たくしゃんのぉおお画像がぁあああ あぉりましゅぅぅぅのぉおおれ、座って作業してぇぇぇぇ゛くらしゃいぃにゃのぉおお！
リズムのぉおお有無にかかわらず演奏したり、インターネットれ自分のぉおお写真を転送したりしゅるのぉおおこともれきましゅぅぅぅ*  - これはぁあああ あぉにゃたのぉおお声れしゅぅぅぅ。[/spoiler]

review:
Z grą spotkałem się po raz pierwszy na PGA.Bardzo dobry tytuł który korzysta z zasady "Łatwe do zrozumienia trudne do wymasterowania".Również warto wspomnieć o muzyce która świetnie oddaje klimat lat 90.Naprawdę polecam zakupić!

Żeby troche pomóc w rozpromowaniu tytułu postanowiłem napisać recenzje na pewnej grupie która napewno ma odbiorców chcących zagrać w to dzieło :)

author: {'steamid': '76561198062394352', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 38, 'playtime_forever': 48, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 48, 'last_played': 1501429143}
review:
If nothing else, it's a demonstration of how to get the most out of your concept. Matching zeros and ones to the display on the screen isn't intrinsically engaging: that comes from the score counter, the combo system and the leaderboards. Even then, though, it didn't hold my attention for too long, but I'd say it's priced appropriately.

TL;DR: lol two-bit control scheme

author: {'steamid': '76561198079883687', 'num_games_owned': 115, 'num_reviews': 6, 'playtime_forever': 220, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 21, 'last_played': 1515007778}
review: I'd say late 90s were a time when Internet was getting slower and slower. Thankfully to some openminded enterpreurs who had shares in local zoos, they employed chimpanzees. I was never feeling needed that much like when playing this game. I recommend it to all network technicians who are making insults at their routers to feel like one and experience what a hard job it is. There is more. You get bananas for this. Who doesn't love bananas? Nobody. Bananas are life.
